title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1982-12-30
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi CR-5A > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab 2448 > CD-Wave (24bit output) > TLH > FLAC 2448 tagged. Transferred by Andrew F. 09/2015
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, Loser-> Little Red Rooster, Big Railroad Blues, Feel Like A Stranger, Dupree's Diamond Blues, The Music Never Stopped-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Touch Of Gray, Throwing Stones-> Franklin's Tower, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Truckin'-> Stella Blue-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Johnny B. Goode, E: Hard To Handle*, E: Tell Mama*

*W Etta James & Tower of Power Horns
